{
  "name": "Invoices",
  "description": "Invoice generation and retrieval endpoints. Invoices are generated as PDF documents from selected line items of an estimate and stored in S3. A presigned URL is returned to allow direct PDF download.",
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Generate Invoice",
      "request": {
        "auth": {
          "type": "bearer",
          "bearer": [
            {
              "key": "token",
              "value": "{{jwt_token}}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n    \"lineItemIds\": [1, 2, 3]\n}",
          "options": {
            "raw": {
              "language": "json"
            }
          }
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/estimates/:estimateId/invoice",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "v1",
            "estimates",
            ":estimateId",
            "invoice"
          ],
          "variable": [
            {
              "key": "estimateId",
              "value": "1",
              "description": "The ID of the estimate to generate an invoice for"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Generate a PDF invoice from selected line items of an estimate. The PDF is stored in S3 and the response includes a presigned URL for direct download.\n\n**Path variable:**\n- `estimateId` (Long): The ID of the estimate\n\n**Required fields:**\n- `lineItemIds` (Array<Long>): IDs of the line items to include in the invoice. Must be non-empty and all must belong to the specified estimate.\n\n**Response:** Returns the created invoice record including a presigned S3 URL to download the generated PDF.\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST \"{{base_url}}/api/v1/estimates/1/invoice\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"lineItemIds\": [1, 2, 3]\n  }'\n```"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "Generate Invoice - Success",
